name: Freddie Sanchez
body:
### Github Page Setup
I'm excited to be using Markdown to craft a simple site to track my current and future projects! Previously, my development has been ad-hoc and random. This page will give each project a new face making each more user friendly.

Look for future articles as I progress with building a [Versal Gadget](https://versal.com/develop-gadgets) based off the [gadget intro](https://github.com/Versal/gadget-dev-intro).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
